---
title: Homestyle Chicken & Creamy Sauce with Mashed Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: The star of tonight's meal is this homestyle sauce; velvety cream is gently infused with chicken stock to make a sauce that pairs
perfectly with chicken and fluffy potato mash. You simply won’t believe you made this amazing meal at home!
